---
// 실제 앱 이미지 없어도 제품 느낌이 나도록 HTML로 목업 렌더링
---

<section class="bg-base-100 py-24 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <span class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary">미리보기</span>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-base-content sm:text-4xl lg:text-[2.75rem]">
        이런 느낌으로<br />쓰게 될 거예요.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-base-content/60">
        실제 스크린샷은 출시와 함께 공개됩니다. 아래는 UI 느낌을 보여주는 미리보기입니다.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <!-- 화면 1: 홈 / 채팅 -->
      <div class="reveal mx-auto w-full max-w-[260px]">
        <div class="relative rounded-[2.5rem] border-[10px] border-neutral bg-neutral p-0.5 shadow-2xl shadow-neutral/20">
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] bg-base-100">
            <!-- 노치 -->
            <div class="relative flex h-6 items-center justify-center bg-neutral">
              <div class="h-4 w-20 rounded-b-2xl bg-neutral"></div>
            </div>
            <!-- 본문 -->
            <div class="h-[480px] overflow-hidden bg-base-200/50 p-4">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <div class="text-[11px] font-bold text-base-content/60">4월 17일</div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full bg-base-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-semibold text-base-content">
                  <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-success"></span>
                  AI
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
                <div class="flex justify-end">
                  <div class="max-w-[75%] rounded-2xl rounded-br-md bg-primary px-3 py-2 text-[11px] font-medium text-primary-content">
                    어제 점심 12000원
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-start">
                  <div class="max-w-[75%] rounded-2xl rounded-bl-md bg-base-100 px-3 py-2 text-[11px] text-base-content shadow-sm">
                    기록했어요 ✓
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-xl border border-base-300 bg-base-100 p-2.5 shadow-sm">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                      <div class="flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-secondary/10 text-[11px]">🍱</div>
                      <div>
                        <div class="text-[11px] font-bold">식비</div>
                        <div class="text-[9px] text-base-content/50">점심</div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-[11px] font-bold tabular-nums">-12,000</div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex justify-end">
                  <div class="max-w-[75%] rounded-2xl rounded-br-md bg-primary px-3 py-2 text-[11px] font-medium text-primary-content">
                    저녁에 택시 15000원도
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-1 px-2">
                  <div class="h-1 w-1 animate-bounce rounded-full bg-base-content/30"></div>
                  <div class="h-1 w-1 animate-bounce rounded-full bg-base-content/30" style="animation-delay: 150ms"></div>
                  <div class="h-1 w-1 animate-bounce rounded-full bg-base-content/30" style="animation-delay: 300ms"></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4 flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-base-300 bg-base-100 px-3 py-2 shadow-lg">
                <span class="flex-1 text-[11px] text-base-content/40">오늘 지출을 입력해보세요</span>
                <div class="flex h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary">
                  <svg class="h-2.5 w-2.5 text-primary-content" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13"/><polygon points="22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2"/></svg>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-base-content">대화로 기록</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-center text-xs text-base-content/50">한 줄이면 끝</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 화면 2: 리포트 -->
      <div class="reveal mx-auto w-full max-w-[260px] md:mt-10" style="animation-delay: 0.15s">
        <div class="relative rounded-[2.5rem] border-[10px] border-neutral bg-neutral p-0.5 shadow-2xl shadow-neutral/20">
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] bg-base-100">
            <div class="relative flex h-6 items-center justify-center bg-neutral">
              <div class="h-4 w-20 rounded-b-2xl bg-neutral"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="h-[480px] overflow-hidden bg-base-200/50 p-4">
              <div class="text-[11px] font-bold text-base-content/60">4월 리포트</div>

              <div class="mt-3 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-accent p-4 text-primary-content">
                <div class="text-[10px] opacity-80">이번 달 지출</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-2xl font-black tabular-nums">847,300<span class="text-sm">원</span></div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-[10px] opacity-80">지난달보다 12,400원 ↑</div>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-4 flex items-end gap-1.5 h-24">
                <div class="w-full rounded-t-sm bg-primary/30" style="height: 35%"></div>
                <div class="w-full rounded-t-sm bg-primary/50" style="height: 55%"></div>
                <div class="w-full rounded-t-sm bg-primary" style="height: 85%"></div>
                <div class="w-full rounded-t-sm bg-primary/70" style="height: 70%"></div>
                <div class="w-full rounded-t-sm bg-primary/40" style="height: 45%"></div>
                <div class="w-full rounded-t-sm bg-primary/60" style="height: 60%"></div>
                <div class="w-full rounded-t-sm bg-primary/35" style="height: 40%"></div>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-4 space-y-2">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg bg-base-100 p-2">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-xs">🍱</span>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold">식비</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-[10px] font-bold tabular-nums">342,000</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg bg-base-100 p-2">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-xs">🚇</span>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold">교통</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-[10px] font-bold tabular-nums">128,400</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg bg-base-100 p-2">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-xs">☕</span>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold">카페</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-[10px] font-bold tabular-nums">47,300</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-base-content">월별 리포트</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-center text-xs text-base-content/50">AI가 먼저 정리</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 화면 3: 검색 -->
      <div class="reveal mx-auto w-full max-w-[260px]" style="animation-delay: 0.3s">
        <div class="relative rounded-[2.5rem] border-[10px] border-neutral bg-neutral p-0.5 shadow-2xl shadow-neutral/20">
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] bg-base-100">
            <div class="relative flex h-6 items-center justify-center bg-neutral">
              <div class="h-4 w-20 rounded-b-2xl bg-neutral"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="h-[480px] overflow-hidden bg-base-200/50 p-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-base-100 px-3 py-2 shadow-sm">
                <svg class="h-3 w-3 text-base-content/40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.34-4.34"/></svg>
                <span class="text-[11px] font-medium text-base-content">지난주 식비 얼마였어?</span>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-4 rounded-2xl bg-base-100 p-4 shadow-sm">
                <div class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-base-content/50">4/8 - 4/14</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-xl font-black tabular-nums">82,400<span class="text-sm">원</span></div>
                <div class="mt-2 text-[10px] text-base-content/60">
                  하루 평균 <span class="font-bold">11,770원</span>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-3 h-px bg-base-300"></div>

                <div class="mt-3 space-y-1.5">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-[10px]">
                    <span class="text-base-content/70">🍱 점심</span>
                    <span class="font-bold tabular-nums">48,000원</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-[10px]">
                    <span class="text-base-content/70">🍚 저녁</span>
                    <span class="font-bold tabular-nums">24,400원</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-[10px]">
                    <span class="text-base-content/70">🥖 간식</span>
                    <span class="font-bold tabular-nums">10,000원</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-dashed border-base-300 p-3 text-[10px] text-base-content/60">
                💡 지난주보다 <span class="font-bold text-secondary">18% 많아요</span>. 점심값이 늘었어요.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-base-content">AI 검색</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-center text-xs text-base-content/50">질문하면 답해줘요</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
